I am creating a blast database of the S. rivoliana genome assemblies.
I am working in the 00_S.rivolianaGenomeAssemblies folder because this is where the S.rivolianaGenomeAssemblies file is located.

Steps:
1. Create a database using the following code:
  1. makeblastdb -in S.rivolianaGenomeAssemblies -dbtype nucl -input_type fasta -out SerRivdb
  2. Output:
    1. Building a new DB, current time: 11/15/2019 12:20:36
